snippet.title: Fighters Uncaged - Launch trailer [Europe]
snippet.description:
More info on http://www.fightersuncaged.com.
Check out this trailer and enter the vicious world of illegal fighting. Be prepared for an all-out brawl through gritty streets and hidden arenas where your body and mettle are your only weapons!
